game.name: Picnic Kabobs: Sara’s Cooking Class
game.description:
Summer is coming and you obviously want to learn some new recipe to make your vacation wonderful. Sara cooking class will not disappoint you if you are eager to learn such a new recipe that could make the fun of your holiday double.  In this exciting and challenging free online cooking game, you will get a chance to learn how to cook yummy kabobs in just a few minutes. Do not waste your time anymore! All you need to do is follow the Sara instructions to complete the task perfectly. 

Sara is an expert cook who actually loves to share her recipe with people who have craving for some unique yet delicious food items. In this cool flash game right from the series Saras Cooking Class, your best friend Sara will explain to you how easier it is to prepare picnic kabobs for your family and friends. You should use the needed kitchen tools and follow the instructions  Sara gives to give your best. Your cooking skills and time management skills are also required to win this exciting cool cooking game for girls.

Picnic kabobs are another fun recipe that is extremely delicious and could make your picnic time more interesting and memorable. You would surely enjoy when cook with beautiful Sara who has an inherent trait of cooking. You would not be able to restrict yourself from trying this mouthwatering recipe at your home once you play this free online game. In order to enjoy the taste of this fabulous picnic kabobs, you are free to try out this in your real kitchen with an adult. All the best for a safe gameplay!
